&lt;p&gt;Hi everyone,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please join us for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Geodynamics Seminar&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Seismology Seminar Room (seismology 2nd floor)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;this coming&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Monday, October 28th&amp;nbsp;at 2 pm&lt;/strong&gt;. Hanchao Jian from the Woods Hole Oceanographic Institute will be presenting for us this week. If you would like to meet with the speaker on October 28th, please email Anne B&amp;eacute;cel (annebcl@ldeo.columbia.edu)&amp;nbsp;to set up a time.&lt;/p&gt;
