&lt;p&gt;Get ready for an exhilarating evening of ideas and innovation at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://entrepreneurship.engineering.columbia.edu/fast-pitch" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fast Pitch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;! This in-person event will take place on&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wednesday, November 20th starting at 5:30pm.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fast Pitch is the perfect opportunity to network and showcase your business or project. Whether you&amp;#39;re a seasoned entrepreneur or just starting out, this event is designed to help you connect with like-minded individuals and gain valuable insights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During the event, participants will have the chance to present their ideas in a fast-paced and exciting format. You&amp;#39;ll have 60 seconds to pitch your concept to a diverse audience of professionals, investors, and potential collaborators. Don&amp;#39;t miss this chance to make a lasting impression! Fast Pitch is all about fostering creativity, collaboration, and growth. So, come prepared to engage in lively discussions, exchange ideas, and build meaningful connections.&lt;/p&gt;
