&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&amp;#39;ll learn:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Facts on alternative investment by some of the largest pension funds in the world. One of the major innovations that globally renowned public pension funds made over the last 20&amp;ndash;30 years has been the increased allocation to alternative investments, including private equity and infrastructure.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
●&amp;nbsp;Reasons for the shift toward alternatives. We will explore how they shifted their strategic asset allocation and how this impacted their performance and discuss their challenges in managing alternative assets.&lt;br /&gt;
