&lt;p&gt;Join us for a book talk with the author of &amp;quot;&lt;a href="https://www.dukeupress.edu/capitalist-humanitarianism" target="_blank"&gt;Capitalist Humanitarianism&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;quot; Lucia Hulsether.&lt;/p&gt;
