&lt;p&gt;Join Alice! Health Promotion for a Responsible Event Host Training (REHT). Learning objectives for this training include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Describe the effects of alcohol on the body.&lt;/li&gt;
